<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nicolasl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3517712); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3517712&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569449" alt="NicolasL" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3517712)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nicolasl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3517712); return false;">NicolasL</a></span></p>
<p>进入<a href="/nicolasl-s-personnel-file">人事档案</a>可查看该作者更多作品</p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong>2020年3月2日</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+41</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
